<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV2">
<l>ceḻunīrt taṭattuk kayalmiḷirn tāloppac cēyarikka</l>
<l>ṇaḻunīr tuḷumpa valamaru kiṉṟaṉa vāḻiyarō</l>
<l>muḻunīr mukilvaṇṇaṉ kaṇṇaṉviṇ ṇāṭṭavar mūtuvarān</l>
<l>toḻunī riṇaiyaṭik kēyaṉpu cūṭṭiya cūḻkuḻaṟkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Equal to carps when they leap in a tank with ample water, red-streaked eyes</l>
<l>are perturbed so that tears brim over. May they live, [they eyes] of [her with]</l>
<l>curls surrounding [her face] who wears love for the pair of feet of venerable nature,</l> 
<l>that exists for the elders that are in the land of heaven, of Kaṇṇaṉ, the one with the colour of the entire water clouds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
